    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dominate the Goal Zone</strong>: Outlast your rivals and seize control to score. It’s not about kills—it’s about relentless <strong>control</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in electrifying <strong>1v1 duels</strong>, coordinate devastating <strong>team assaults</strong>, or unleash chaos in massive <strong>multi-team brawls</strong>! Every round is a wild, skill-testing party you won't want to miss. Easy to pick up, impossible to put down—this is a party game from another dimension!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/61e32cafa01cc2c2dd61b6b8ffd4aeb7.avif?t=1770658156\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras_big/61e32cafa01cc2c2dd61b6b8ffd4aeb7.avif?t=1770658156 width=800 height=410 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master the Hammer:</strong> Hurl it, teleport to it, and outsmart your opponents with pinpoint precision and cunning tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/cfa3674167a34a62ca9c1d1c752aaa03.poster.avif?t=1770658156\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/cfa3674167a34a62ca9c1d1c752aaa03.webm?t=1770658156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/cfa3674167a34a62ca9c1d1c752aaa03.mp4?t=1770658156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8-Player Chaos</strong> – Battle it out in fast-paced multiplayer matches with up to 8 players online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/bdaa6e191ee093c00204f8a993ff0995.poster.avif?t=1770658156\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/bdaa6e191ee093c00204f8a993ff0995.webm?t=1770658156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/bdaa6e191ee093c00204f8a993ff0995.mp4?t=1770658156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blast into the Zone:</strong> Team up with friends (online or couch co-op) and brawl your way to freedom through the arcade portal. Battle across vibrant, neon-drenched stages where every punch, jump, and power-up bends the rules of reality. Holding the zone is the key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A World of Secrets</strong> – Beneath the clean and simple surface lies eerie, hidden lore—uncover glimpses of the unknown as you play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/3ed66e6d473a5838df5c6380585cafdc.poster.avif?t=1770658156\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/3ed66e6d473a5838df5c6380585cafdc.webm?t=1770658156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270900/extras/3ed66e6d473a5838df5c6380585cafdc.mp4?t=1770658156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features ITZ:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 8 PLAYERS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your Squad, Your Rules: Play 1v1, 4v4, 1v7, or any combination you can imagine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold the Zone to Win: Forget traditional kills – it's all about controlling the zone. Wield your teleporting boomerang hammer to throw, recall, and warp around the arena!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Couch/Local and Online Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-platform</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 interactive, absurd arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from 12 messed-up Outcasts trapped in the Zone. What could possibly go wrong? (Everything.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brutal Mayhem Guaranteed</p></li></ul>",
